<div tiddler="TodayMacro" modifier="JeremyRuston" modified="200510302315" created="200510302315" tags="macros">The {{{&lt;&lt;today&gt;&gt;}}} macro inserts the current date and time into a tiddler. It's updated each time the tiddler is redisplayed.\n\nIt can optionally take a DateFormatString to determine the way that the date is displayed:\n\n{{{\n&lt;&lt;today&gt;&gt;\n&lt;&lt;today&gt;&gt;\n}}}\n\nResults in:\n&lt;&lt;today&gt;&gt;\n&lt;&lt;today&gt;&gt;\n</div>